page.title: 05My Day (continued)
page.content: In maths we are doing about graphs. {12:00 We go for lunch.I have {sandwichs all the time.In the {playground we play runouts and tig. 13:10 The next lesson is games,my favourate.In games we do rugby, rounders,running,high jump,long jump,football and uni-hoc. {14:15 We have a break again.In last {break we just muck about. 14:30 We have I.S. again.Sometimes we go in the Coppice. {15:30 We go home.I watch the TV until {my tea's ready. Then I read for a bit. 18:00 Nick comes and we go out to play football. {19:30 I go in and play on my computer. 20:30 I go in and watch the TV. {21:30 I go to bed.
